project_descr: PIMS 3642 Sustainable Management of Biodiversity in Thailand's Production Landscape

outputs.output_descr: The project will directly address these barriers through the three major components of the project: 1) Building  national capacity for support of Biodiversity Business; 2) Piloting Community-based Social Enterprises (CbSE) in valuable Eco-regions; and 3) Mainstreaming Biodiversity Business into the supply chains of high-value consumer markets.
